{"id": "nederlandse-glasgroentesector-de-kas-als-kracht__c4-paragraph__0004", "text": "[Jelmer Schreurs](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/authors/jelmer-schreurs/index.html)", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "nederlandse-glasgroentesector-de-kas-als-kracht__c4-paragraph__0004", "source_slug": "nederlandse-glasgroentesector-de-kas-als-kracht", "source_title": "Dutch greenhouse vegetable sector: The greenhouse as a force", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/agrarisch/nederlandse-glasgroentesector-de-kas-als-kracht.html", "source_date": "2025-07-31", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "agrarisch", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 4, "n_chunks_total": 27, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "nederlandse-glasgroentesector-de-kas-als-kracht__c4-paragraph__0005", "text": "The Dutch greenhouse vegetable sector is among the world's best. Greenhouse vegetables are also performing well within the Dutch agricultural sector; the income of the Dutch greenhouse vegetable grower exceeds the agricultural average by a factor of 3. This was not always the case. The sector has changed course since 2011 and strengthened its position in the sales chain. The resulting success factors are entrepreneurship and cooperation on social issues, innovation in the greenhouse, chain integration and strengthening the position in the chain. What is needed to maintain this leading position?", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "nederlandse-glasgroentesector-de-kas-als-kracht__c4-paragraph__0005", "source_slug": "nederlandse-glasgroentesector-de-kas-als-kracht", "source_title": "Dutch greenhouse vegetable sector: The greenhouse as a force", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/agrarisch/nederlandse-glasgroentesector-de-kas-als-kracht.html", "source_date": "2025-07-31", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "agrarisch", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 5, "n_chunks_total": 27, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "nederlandse-glasgroentesector-de-kas-als-kracht__c4-paragraph__0006", "text": "Read all the facts and developments in the report 'Dutch greenhouse vegetable sector: The greenhouse as a force'.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "nederlandse-glasgroentesector-de-kas-als-kracht__c4-paragraph__0006", "source_slug": "nederlandse-glasgroentesector-de-kas-als-kracht", "source_title": "Dutch greenhouse vegetable sector: The greenhouse as a force", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/agrarisch/nederlandse-glasgroentesector-de-kas-als-kracht.html", "source_date": "2025-07-31", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "agrarisch", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 6, "n_chunks_total": 27, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
